name: Rocky Betty
description:
"Dleideans do not necessarily need legs or anything like that, but Rocky loves to skate, so he chooses to adopt some. And yes, every Dleidian is called Betty, so change the surname or the hierarchical function, but always Betty"



this work was created in the pixelpetz game by me (@eitaivan). i produced a series of original alien characters, exploring linking science fiction, fantasy and horror references.
